2014-03-05 22:50:34	--	-
2014-03-05 22:50:34	--	- MORGAN, RICHARD K. (1965-) is an English science fiction
2014-03-05 22:50:34	--	- author. Morgan's books are generally set in a dystopian world.
2014-03-05 22:50:34	--	- His breakout novel Altered Carbon won the Philip K. Dick Award,
2014-03-05 22:50:34	--	- and he has written many successful and amazing works to follow.
2014-03-05 22:50:34	--	- His more recent writings explore the theme of autonomy
2014-03-05 22:50:34	--	- in science fiction and escapism in fantasy.
2014-03-05 22:50:34	--	-
