2014-06-30 14:29:32	--	- card.freenode.net Message of the Day -
2014-06-30 14:29:32	--	-
2014-06-30 14:29:32	--	- Welcome to card.freenode.net in Washington, DC, US, kindly sponsored by
2014-06-30 14:29:32	--	- Team Cymru (http://www.team-cymru.org).
2014-06-30 14:29:32	--	-
2014-06-30 14:29:32	--	- CARD, ORSON SCOTT [1951-].  Born in Richland, Washington, Card grew up in
2014-06-30 14:29:32	--	- California, Arizona, and Utah.  He lived in Brazil for two years as an
2014-06-30 14:29:32	--	- unpaid missionary for the Mormon Church.  Author of the Ender and Alvin
2014-06-30 14:29:32	--	- Maker books, Card's science fiction and fantasy work is strongly influenced
2014-06-30 14:29:32	--	- by his Mormon cultural background.  The first author to win the Hugo and
2014-06-30 14:29:32	--	- Nebula novel awards two years in a row, Card currently lives in Greensboro,
2014-06-30 14:29:32	--	- North Carolina, US.
2014-06-30 14:29:32	--	-
